  {
    "id": "200662070448291_1506867891448817",
    "message": "Imagine you're a monk in the 1700's and you are fasting for the 40 days of Lent.  No food!--but you are allowed to drink....  Enter the Doppelbock.  Our doppelbock is called the Manganator; as a double of our dunkel, it's a meal in a glass.  On tap today!  Hot beer poker on Sunday! #dontfastthough #drinkitforlent #drinkwatertooplease \nVisit Coshocton, Ohio! @visitcoshocton Ohio Craft Beer Northeast Ohio Craft Beverage News",
