  {
    "id": "200662070448291_1506168151518791",
    "message": "Throwback Thursday!  Doppelbocks are traditionally associated with goats, and since we're tapping our doppelbock (the Manganator) this weekend, it seemed a good time to remember the original brewery goat:  Hoppy Phils! He was so cute we ignored all his naughtiness for a long time.... #RIP   #brewerygoats #brewerydogs \nVisit Coshocton, Ohio! @visitcoshocton",
