  {
    "id": "200662070448291_1505242104944729",
    "message": "We're tapping the Manganator on Saturday, and on Sunday, we're poking it with a red-hot poker!  Bierstacheln is an old tradition of gently caramelizing a rich, malty beer with a heated iron poker.  Join us around the fire-pit on Sunday from 12:30-4:30pm for this fun and unique event! #redhotpokerbeer #doppelbock #mealinaglass\n\nVisit Coshocton, Ohio! @visitcoshocton Ohio Craft Beer Northeast Ohio Craft Beverage News",
